{"thag2.22:0.1":"Theragatha 2.22 ","thag2.22:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.22:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.22:0.4":"Bhaddajittheragatha ","thag2.22:1.1":"“Panado nama so raja, ","thag2.22:1.2":"yassa yupo suvannayo; ","thag2.22:1.3":"Tiriyam solasubbedho, ","thag2.22:1.4":"ubbhamahu sahassadha. ","thag2.22:2.1":"Sahassakando satagendu, ","thag2.22:2.2":"dhajalu haritamayo; ","thag2.22:2.3":"Anaccum tattha gandhabba, ","thag2.22:2.4":"chasahassani sattadha”ti. ","thag2.22:2.5":"… Bhaddajitthero …. "}